column44: To have more informal outings/special programs with members to engage with members.

Good job done thus far. Love the Club. It is fun. It is entertaining. It is educational. It is inspiring. On a serious note, similar to what's done for Cenviro, MTMC can do more outreach to smaller secretarial firms / in house CS teams to boost membership.
MTMC is blessed to have passionate members to continue to fuel the meetings. Hybrid meetings are well and seamlessly arranged. Once a year off-site meeting is continued to enhance fellowship.
The club has several distinguished toastmasters and their unwavering support is the pillar of the club
To encourage more old members to join the meeting, to bring benefit to the new members.
Our club have been stable and strong in all respects
Get more new members and advertise regularly in social media.
